data.description: Wonderful home on over 2 acres, very private! Home offers a beautiful kitchen. It has white cabinets, quartz slab countertops, the perfect backsplash, high end SS appliances, large island w/farm style sink & touch faucet. Dining room off kitchen. Family room with stacked stone fireplace, wood floors throughout down stairs. Large den/office on main level. There is also a full bath with tub/shower combo on main level as well. Upstairs has large owners suite, walk-in closet, plus double vanities, soaking tub, & shower. There are 2 other bedrooms plus a hall bath, double sinks, and laundry in hall as well. Plus a huge bonus room with closet, could serve as many options. The screened porch is great and leads to the backyard which has endless possibilities. 2 car garage is oversized with plenty of storage. Easy access to crawl space. Great value in Lenoir City!
